To refresh it:

1. Create a mirror folder
2. Put the mirror.list inside, modify it according to your configuration
3. Run apt-mirror ./mirror.list
4. Generate the Contents-amd64.gz with `apt-ftparchive contents ./ > Contents-amd64 && gzip -f Contents-amd64`
5. Put the Contents-amd64.gz in mirror/â€¦/dists/xenial/main/
6. Run `dep11-generator process . xenial`
7. Enjoy!

